high_descs: Walk around the kitchen island to the sink.
Pick up the tomato out of the sink.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the oven and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the tomato inside then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave and take the now heated tomato out.
Walk over to the fridge behind you.
Open the fridge and put the heated tomato inside, then close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and go towards the wall, then turn left and go forward, then go to the sink adjacent to the dishwasher.
Pick up a tomato from the sink.
Turn around and move forward, then turn left toward the stove and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside and heat it, then take it out.
Turn around and go to the wall ahead, then turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato inside, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Make a left and walk around the island to face the sink.
Pick up the tomato from the sink.
Make a right to walk to the microwave above the stove.
Heat the tomato up in the microwave, removing it again.
Make a left and walk back towards the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a tomato in the microwave to put in the fridge.
